- Change mission params â†’ All areas re-validate

âœ… **Smart Scaling**
- Mission duration affects required area
- Short mission (30 days): 1.0x multiplier
- Medium mission (180 days): 1.1x multiplier
- Long mission (365+ days): 1.3x multiplier

âœ… **Intelligent Feedback**
- Too small â†’ Red border + error message
- Slightly small â†’ Yellow border + warning
- Meets requirements â†’ Green border + checkmark

âœ… **NASA Compliance**
